Greenlight Capital Re Ltd. (GLRE) , the
reinsurer whose largest shareholder is  David Einhorn , picked
chief underwriting officer Bart Hedges to succeed Chief
Executive Officer Leonard Goldberg when he retires in August.  Goldberg has served as CEO since August 2005, the Cayman
Islands-based company said today in a statement distributed by
Globe Newswire.  To contact the reporter on this story:
